name: TY+Die Tank
description:
Tie then Dye, then see what happens? That's what we did when we started experimenting with dyes and came up with this culmination of a beauty. We love the unique patterns and effects that come from this process and knew that we had to do a Tie dye shirt. Each hand-picked colour fuses together to create a fresh new vibe of what is an old process. Each piece is totally unique and is individually hand dyed to create a truly one-of-a-kind pattern. Not just limited to hippies and stoners this tank will brighten the life of anyone.

Limited Supply.

NOTE: Each piece is hand dyed and unique so they will all vary from the one shown in the picture.
